# AuditIQ secrets.
# - Local Streamlit run: copy this file to `.streamlit/secrets.toml` and fill in your key.
# - Streamlit Community Cloud: paste these lines into the "Secrets" box (Advanced settings).
# NEVER commit your real secrets.toml (it is gitignored). app.py bridges these into env vars.

